[div class=p 
	"Time savers that didn't work out in the final version:
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		"	In my earlier versions, in the second screen of 4-3, I jumped over the knife-thrower and was able to bounce off his knife at the exit. This was 2 frames faster than what you see in this version, but after I changed the level three boss fight, I could not get it to line up.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		"	Sometimes, depending on when you exit the previous screen (or probably more precisely, when the boss screen loads... but that can't be directly manipulated) the timer for the boss fight will appear a few frames sooner. This, predictably, results in the timer reaching zero sooner, which means that the cinema screen starts three frames sooner. This happened for the Kelbeross (level 4), Masked Devil and Jaquio battles in my previous versions but I wasn't so lucky in this final version.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
